revision.text: ==English== ===Alternative forms=== * [[yam-stick]] * [[yam stick]] ===Etymology=== {{compound|en|yam|stick}} ===Noun=== {{en-noun}} # A rod-shaped implement used by the [[aboriginal]] people of Australia to dig [[yam]] and as a combat weapon. #: ''She thrust her '''yamstick''' into the hard ground to reach the prized tuber.'' ===Anagrams=== * {{anagrams|en|a=acikmsty|kymatics}}
